{"tid":2171024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE擬停考《六國論》英保守黨人都識：「弊在賂秦」","createTime":"2020-08-23T16:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T01:59:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f27532e25e7b7aeb4e57aeb8f1382dc6f8f8d7","tid":2171024,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"「六國破滅，非兵不利，戰不善，弊在賂秦。」一唸起頭四句，幾乎老中青都識背埋落去&hellip;&hellip;或者係背多幾句。緊接嗰幾句係「賂秦而力虧，破滅之道也。或曰：『六國互喪，率賂秦耶？』曰：『不賂者以賂者喪。』蓋失強援，不能獨完，故曰『弊在賂秦』也。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/JBVYT5NGGBADFPKBVDFVJGYKSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FJBVYT5NGGBADFPKBVDFVJGYKSI%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzspzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=cd29c439\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FJBVYT5NGGBADFPKBVDFVJGYKSI%2F&h=b81719d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/JBVYT5NGGBADFPKBVDFVJGYKSI/</a>"},{"pid":"d79de63da2def5f96f0e56fd55e07c548fe92552","tid":2171024,"uid":244152,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"歐美破滅，非兵不利，戰不善，弊在賂共。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47df783c194bcd3b94d7c299b9255b3a816f0781","tid":2171024,"uid":185424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d79de63da2def5f96f0e56fd55e07c548fe92552","tid":2171024,"uid":244152,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"歐美破滅，非兵不利，戰不善，弊在賂共。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"歷史不繼重覆<br />\n但願我們這一代可以見証支共倒台的一刻"},{"pid":"77604365f30024d80063d8d5871ec7ffc2237fe8","tid":2171024,"uid":173072,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:24:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"329c61f09f85728d5681e7dd0489484d48d8eead","tid":2171024,"uid":230146,"like":1,